      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/who-is-simon-sadler-the-block-trade-king-has-amassed-360-million-wealth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西蒙·萨德勒 (Simon Sadler) 将 Segantii Capital Management Ltd. 从一家小型初创对冲基金转变为一家价值 48 亿美元的巨头，并在香港建立了亚洲“大宗交易之王”的声誉。]]></description>
