      <title>Vanguard 与 Pimco 一起认为日本央行加息幅度高于市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/vanguard-joins-pimco-in-seeing-more-boj-rate-hikes-than-market</link>
